enhanced_by.reason: The generateValid method generates valid SSNs that can be used as inputs for testing isValidSwedishSsn.
The generateInvalid method generates invalid SSNs that can be used as inputs for testing isValidSwedishSsn.
The parseDate method is invoked within isValidSwedishSsn to validate the date part of the SSN, making it a necessary precondition.
The calculateChecksum method is invoked within isValidSwedishSsn to validate the checksum of the SSN, making it a necessary precondition.
